query:
SELECT g.id, g.title, COUNT(gp.id) as package_count 
FROM gigs g 
LEFT JOIN gigPackages gp ON g.id = gp.gigId 
GROUP BY g.id 
HAVING package_count > 0 
LIMIT 5
